[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "はぁ～、火って落ち着くわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00000",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（思えばここまで色々あったわ。\n　果ての大陸を目指してたどり着いた暗黒の氷海――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00001",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（そこで見つけた「九偉人図」の切れ端。\n　これを完成させるのが果ての大陸へ渡る鍵……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00002",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（最後は私の兄と姉にあたるヘルトとゼロと戦って\n　すべての「九偉人図」と、兄弟が揃った）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00003",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（あとは「九偉人図」が指示した場所、暗黒の氷海に\n　もう一度乗り込むだけ！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00004",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "色々あったけど、兄弟みんなで\n協力できることになって、よかった……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00005",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "しみじみしてるところ悪いんだけど、\nだからって全員うちに招かれても困るんですがねえ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00006",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "うっ……いやあ、みんな私が暮らしてる家を見たいって\n聞かないもんだから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00007",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "あと、焼いといてって頼んでたマシュマロは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00008",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……美味しかったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00009",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "この食いしん坊に頼んだ私が悪かったわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00010",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "こちらが無理言って押し掛けたんだ。\nもてなそうとしなくても構わない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_038_00011",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "だね。こうして外で食べるのも乙なもんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_038_00012",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "あれもこれもうまいのう！\nいくらでも食べられそうじゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_038_00013",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "えへへっ、ありがとうございます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_052_038_00014",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "フロッケちゃん、\n私もお料理運ぶの、手伝うよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_038_00015",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "はい、どうぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_038_00016",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "悪くない。まあ、俺の料理にはかなわないがな。\nそうだろ、シトリン？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00017",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "さあ？　ヘルトのスープは思い出の味ってだけで、\n料理自体はフロッケのほうが上手いと思うけど？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_038_00018",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "なんだと……言ってくれるじゃないか。\nフロッケ、後でこれのレシピを教えろ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_038_00019",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "はいっ、フロッケにできることなら！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_052_038_00020",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "美味しそうな匂い……またお腹空いてきちゃった！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00021",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "つまみ食いしといてこれかよ……\nあんまり食べるとランツェやフロッケの分もなくなるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00022",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あれ？　そういえばランツェは？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00023",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "呼んだか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00024",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "おぉ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00025",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ランツェのくせに……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00026",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "るせぇ、似合わねえのは分かってるよ！　果ての大陸\n出航記念式典に出るからには正装が必要なんだっての！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00027",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "いや、似合ってないとは言ってないって。\nむしろかっこいい、決まってるって言おうとしたのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00028",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "それじゃいつもの格好が\nかっこ悪いってことになるだろうが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00029",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そんなことないって！　シブいよ、いつものも！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00030",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "しかし、記念式典かあ……いよいよ果ての大陸への\n出発が近づいてきてるのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00031",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "ああ、準備は万全だ。行けっていうなら\n今からだって漕ぎ出せるぜ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00032",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "その服で指揮をとるのはキツいんじゃないの、船長",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00033",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "動きづれぇ！って、服を破きだしたりして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00034",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "するか！　大切な一張羅だぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00035",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "確認できましたね。ヴァレリアのもう１つの家族が",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_038_00036",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "肯定……楽しそうで何より",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_038_00037",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]